title: Looking for team
body: Im a bronze 1 player mostly support but i do play mid and jng. If you have any questions add me on league @ captainfatcake

replies.body: Hey I'm a Bronze 1 ADC/support. I have only gotten back into the game recently after a few seasons break. Used to be Silver 1 when I played.

Hey we have a high diamond/challenger team.... we are looking for a good support player I think you could the one!!!
Add me on league this is your chance to go pro!!
You will have infinitely more success here: https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com
